{"tid":2142352,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【恭 喜】黨鐵業績｜港鐵上半年虧損逾3億元　乘客量大跌38%","createTime":"2020-08-06T10:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T15:17:19.000Z","uid":293677,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2c95b6c72f8bf22efa5329d6e6b29b25093907e3","tid":2142352,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T10:54:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/5008218/org/7e3c4289c494865b2c0687720774811e.jpg/9JLDdA6e58jvgQzSBtUGqsUoVun-085GnopP5Z6KT-U?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F5008218%2Forg%2F7e3c4289c494865b2c0687720774811e.jpg%2F9JLDdA6e58jvgQzSBtUGqsUoVun-085GnopP5Z6KT-U%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=bb79ad11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵今日（6日）下午舉行中期業績會，受新冠肺炎疫情影響下，其客量大跌，商場租務亦受影響，整體營運都受挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵行政總裁金澤培表示，港鐵在疫情下，需應對起伏不定的衝擊，前景不明朗。<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">上半年虧損3.34億元，總乘客量按年跌38%，當中由於疫情而停駛的城際客運及高鐵香港段跌幅最大，分別下跌91.7%及89.4%。</span></span>不過金澤培強調，港鐵整體財政仍然穩健。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eVu9DNx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeVu9DNx.gif&h=8c074a6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e390afbccc423f1b3ec15822577a19c8b3b54335","tid":2142352,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T10:54:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/507649/%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%A5%AD%E7%B8%BE-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E8%99%A7%E6%90%8D%E9%80%BE3%E5%84%84%E5%85%83-%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E9%87%8F%E5%A4%A7%E8%B7%8C38\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F507649%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF